title: Raychel Sun
text: I am a PhD candidate in Political Science at the University of Florida, specializing in computational social science research and international political economy. I love finding patterns in complex data and turning them into clear, actionable insights.

title: Publication
text:
Gender and the Great Resignation, Phenomenal World, January 28, 2023

Hidden Burdens: How Family Responsibilities and Job Insecurity Shape Women’s Trade Protectionism, The British International Studies Association 2023 Conference, June 20, 2023
Assessing the Impacts of the COVID-19 Recession and the Great Recession in the US, 79th Annual Midwest Political Science Association Conference, April 08, 2022
